ente o Bilhete original;</span></span></li>\n<li>Caso não tenha o Bilhete original, a cópia do Bilhete também serve.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=”4.11.3″ _module_preset=”default” min_height=”96px” custom_padding=”23px||0px|||” global_colors_info=”{}”]</p>\n<h3 class="et_pb_module_header et-fb-editable-element et-fb-editable-element__editing" contenteditable="true" data-quickaccess-id="header" data-shortcode-id="0.1.0.0-1639051415197" style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">REQUISITOS NECESSÁRIOS PARA A </span></span><u><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">EMISSÃO DO CERTIFICADO DE REGISTO CRIMINAL</span></span></span></span></u></h3>\n<p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=”4.11.3″ _module_preset=”default” width=”100%” max_width=”100%” min_height=”0px” custom_margin=”0px|0px|0px|35px|false|false” custom_padding=”4px|0px|0px|0px|false|false” global_colors_info=”{}”]</p>\n<ul>\n<li style="list-style-type: none;"></li>\n<li><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">O Certificado de Registo Criminal para os Cidadãos nacionais é emitido com base no Bilhete de Identidade original e válido;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n<li><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">O Certificado de Registo Cr