30) 240 89 755-20<br>\n<strong>Fax:</strong> (+49 30) 240 89 712<br>\n<strong>Email:</strong> sector.consular@botschaftangola.de</p>\n\n<p>Applicants should submit their requests well in advance. Prior appointment is recommended for in-person attendance.</p>	Consular services of the Embassy of the Republic of Angola in Berlin	\N	\N	\N	\N	2026-02-20 15:40:09.542997+00	\N	\N	\N	0
